Package: climateAnalyzeR
Title: Import Data from ClimateAnalyzer.org into R
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Van Scoyoc",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "matthew_vanscoyoc@nps.org",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6821-4476"))
Description: This package creates a brief climate report for National Park 
    Service Co-op Stations and imports data from ClimateAnalyzer.org into R. 
    Data abailable to import are temperature, precipitation, and soil water 
    balance models.
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0)
